â€œWe use the reverse technique.
First reverse the entire array, then reverse the first k elements, and finally reverse the remaining elements.
This gives us the rotated array in-place without extra memory.â€

â±ï¸ TIME & SPACE COMPLEXITY
Type	Value
Time	O(n)
Space	O(1) (in-place)

